{"sn12.2:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 12.2 ","sn12.2:0.2":"1. Buddhavagga ","sn12.2:0.3":"Vibhangasutta ","sn12.2:1.1":"Savatthiyam viharati. ","sn12.2:1.2":"“Paticcasamuppadam vo, bhikkhave, desessami vibhajissami. ","sn12.2:1.3":"Tam sunatha, sadhukam manasi karotha, bhasissami”ti. ","sn12.2:1.4":"“Evam, bhante”ti kho te bhikkhu bhagavato paccassosum. ","sn12.2:1.5":"Bhagava etadavoca: ","sn12.2:2.1":"“Katamo ca, bhikkhave, paticcasamuppado? ","sn12.2:2.2":"Avijjapaccaya, bhikkhave, sankhara; ","sn12.2:2.3":"sankharapaccaya vinnanam; ","sn12.2:2.4":"vinnanapaccaya namarupam; ","sn12.2:2.5":"namarupapaccaya salayatanam; ","sn12.2:2.6":"salayatanapaccaya phasso; ","sn12.2:2.7":"phassapaccaya vedana; ","sn12.2:2.8":"vedanapaccaya tanha; ","sn12.2:2.9":"tanhapaccaya upadanam; ","sn12.2:2.10":"upadanapaccaya bhavo; ","sn12.2:2.11":"bhavapaccaya jati; ","sn12.2:2.12":"jatipaccaya jaramaranam sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupayasa sambhavanti. ","sn12.2:2.13":"Evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti. ","sn12.2:3.1":"Katamanca, bhikkhave, jaramaranam? ","sn12.2:3.2":"Ya tesam tesam sattanam tamhi tamhi sattanikaye jara jiranata khandiccam paliccam valittacata ayuno samhani indriyanam paripako; ","sn12.2:3.3":"ayam vuccati jara. ","sn12.2:3.4":"Ya tesam tesam sattanam tamha tamha sattanikaya cuti cavanata bhedo antaradhanam maccu maranam kalakiriya khandhanam bhedo kalevarassa nikkhepo (…), ","sn12.2:3.5":"idam vuccati maranam. ","sn12.2:3.6":"Iti ayanca jara, idanca maranam. ","sn12.2:3.7":"Idam vuccati, bhikkhave, jaramaranam. ","sn12.2:4.1":"Katama ca, bhikkhave, jati? ","sn12.2:4.2":"Ya tesam tesam sattanam tamhi tamhi sattanikaye jati sanjati okkanti abhinibbatti khandhanam patubhavo ayatananam patilabho. ","sn12.2:4.3":"Ayam vuccati, bhikkhave, jati. ","sn12.2:5.1":"Katamo ca, bhikkhave, bhavo? ","sn12.2:5.2":"Tayome, bhikkhave, bhava—","sn12.2:5.3":"kamabhavo, rupabhavo, arupabhavo. ","sn12.2:5.4":"Ayam vuccati, bhikkhave, bhavo. ","sn12.2:6.1":"Katamanca, bhikkhave, upadanam? ","sn12.2:6.2":"Cattarimani, bhikkhave, upadanani—","sn12.2:6.3":"kamupadanam, ditthupadanam, silabbatupadanam, attavadupadanam. ","sn12.2:6.4":"Idam vuccati, bhikkhave, upadanam. ","sn12.2:7.1":"Katama ca, bhikkhave, tanha? ","sn12.2:7.2":"Chayime, bhikkhave, tanhakaya—","sn12.2:7.3":"rupatanha, saddatanha, gandhatanha, rasatanha, photthabbatanha, dhammatanha. ","sn12.2:7.4":"Ayam vuccati, bhikkhave, tanha. ","sn12.2:8.1":"Katama ca, bhikkhave, vedana? ","sn12.2:8.2":"Chayime, bhikkhave, vedanakaya—","sn12.2:8.3":"cakkhusamphassaja vedana, sotasamphassaja vedana, ghanasamphassaja vedana, jivhasamphassaja vedana, kayasamphassaja vedana, manosamphassaja vedana. ","sn12.2:8.4":"Ayam vuccati, bhikkhave, vedana. ","sn12.2:9.1":"Katamo ca, bhikkhave, phasso? ","sn12.2:9.2":"Chayime, bhikkhave, phassakaya—","sn12.2:9.3":"cakkhusamphasso, sotasamphasso, ghanasamphasso, jivhasamphasso, kayasamphasso, manosamphasso. ","sn12.2:9.4":"Ayam vuccati, bhikkhave, phasso. ","sn12.2:10.1":"Katamanca, bhikkhave, salayatanam? ","sn12.2:10.2":"Cakkhayatanam, sotayatanam, ghanayatanam, jivhayatanam, kayayatanam, manayatanam—","sn12.2:10.3":"idam vuccati, bhikkhave, salayatanam. ","sn12.2:11.1":"Katamanca, bhikkhave, namarupam? ","sn12.2:11.2":"Vedana, sanna, cetana, phasso, manasikaro—","sn12.2:11.3":"idam vuccati namam. ","sn12.2:11.4":"Cattaro ca mahabhuta, catunnanca mahabhutanam upadayarupam. ","sn12.2:11.5":"Idam vuccati rupam. ","sn12.2:11.6":"Iti idanca namam, idanca rupam. ","sn12.2:11.7":"Idam vuccati, bhikkhave, namarupam. ","sn12.2:12.1":"Katamanca, bhikkhave, vinnanam? ","sn12.2:12.2":"Chayime, bhikkhave, vinnanakaya—","sn12.2:12.3":"cakkhuvinnanam, sotavinnanam, ghanavinnanam, jivhavinnanam, kayavinnanam, manovinnanam. ","sn12.2:12.4":"Idam vuccati, bhikkhave, vinnanam. ","sn12.2:13.1":"Katame ca, bhikkhave, sankhara? ","sn12.2:13.2":"Tayome, bhikkhave, sankhara—","sn12.2:13.3":"kayasankharo, vacisankharo, cittasankharo. ","sn12.2:13.4":"Ime vuccanti, bhikkhave, sankhara. ","sn12.2:14.1":"Katama ca, bhikkhave, avijja? ","sn12.2:14.2":"Yam kho, bhikkhave, dukkhe annanam, dukkhasamudaye annanam, dukkhanirodhe annanam, dukkhanirodhagaminiya patipadaya annanam. ","sn12.2:14.3":"Ayam vuccati, bhikkhave, avijja. ","sn12.2:15.1":"Iti kho, bhikkhave, avijjapaccaya sankhara; ","sn12.2:15.2":"sankharapaccaya vinnanam …pe… ","sn12.2:15.3":"evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti. ","sn12.2:15.4":"Avijjaya tveva asesaviraganirodha sankharanirodho; ","sn12.2:15.5":"sankharanirodha vinnananirodho …pe… ","sn12.2:15.6":"evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hoti”ti. ","sn12.2:15.7":"Dutiyam. "}